OL,3,CProsecutors demand 20-year sentence
OL,4,Cfor ex-husband in mass rape trial
OL,6,FFrench prosecutors have demanded the
OL,7,Fmaximum prison sentence of 20 years
OL,8,Ffor Dominique Pelicot, who is accused
OL,9,Fof drugging his ex-wife and organising
OL,10,Ffor more than 50 men to rape her while
OL,11,Fshe lay unconscious.
OL,13,FLaure Chabaud told the courthouse in
OL,14,FAvignon, southern France, on Monday
OL,15,Fthat the sentence would be "long" but
OL,16,F"not enough considering the serious
OL,17,Fnature of these acts" against Gisele
OL,18,FPelicot.
