OL,6,F"There are many examples in history of
OL,7,Fcriminals capable of presenting
OL,8,Fthemselves in a charming light and who
OL,9,Fat the same time are capable of the
OL,10,Fworst atrocities. Dominique Pelicot
OL,11,Ffits this bill. He was an attentive
OL,12,Fhusband, father and grandfather," Ms
OL,13,FChabaud said.
OL,15,F"He suffers from no mental illness, so
OL,16,Fhe is fully responsible for the acts
OL,17,Fhe committed," the prosecutor added.
OL,19,FJournalists and supporters gathered in
OL,20,Fthe courtroom on Monday morning for
OL,21,Fthe final day of arguments.
