OL,6,FPelicot has been accused of organising
OL,7,Ffor more than 50 men to visit his
OL,8,Fhouse and rape his wife, Gisele
OL,9,FPelicot.
OL,11,FOver a period spanning nearly ten
OL,12,Fyears, Dominique Pelicot used an
OL,13,Fonline website and messaging platforms
OL,14,Fto seek out men. He admitted to
OL,15,Fhabitually drugging his wife with a
OL,16,Fstrong sedative before allowing
OL,17,Fstrangers to sexually abuse her.
