OL,6,FPelicot kept his eyes closed and
OL,7,Flooked down at the ground during the
OL,8,Fhearing - all 50 other defendants were
OL,9,Falso present in court, with many using
OL,10,Fface masks to conceal their faces from
OL,11,Fthe cameras.
OL,13,FThe case has sparked a debate about
OL,14,Fattitudes in France towards consent.
OL,15,FThroughout the court case that began
OL,16,Fin September, defence lawyers for
OL,17,FPelicot have tried to undermine Gisele
OL,18,FPelicot's claim that she was unaware
OL,19,Fof her husband's actions.
