OL,6,FThe prosecutor highlighted the issue
OL,7,Fagain in court on Monday, saying: "We
OL,8,Fcan't say in 2024 that because she
OL,9,F(Gisele Pelicot) didn't say anything
OL,10,Fshe consented."
OL,12,F"There was nothing ambiguous about
OL,13,FGisele Pelicot that could make the men
OL,14,Fthink she was giving her consent," Ms
OL,15,FChabaud added.
