OL,6,FMs Chabaud told the court on Monday
OL,7,Fthat she didn't want to return to the
OL,8,F"question that keeps coming up, 'how
OL,9,Fis it possible that she (Gisele
OL,10,FPelicot) didn't realise anything was
OL,11,Fgoing on?'"
OL,13,F"For years, she tried to understand
OL,14,Fwhat was wrong with her, she had pains
OL,15,Fin her lower abdomen, vaginal
OL,16,Fdischarge, hemorrhoids and so on. No
OL,17,Fanalysis was able to determine the
OL,18,Fcause," the prosecutor added.
