OL,6,FThe court is expected to deliver its
OL,7,Fverdicts before December 20, in what
OL,8,Fis considered to be one of the darkest
OL,9,Fcriminal cases in modern French
OL,10,Fhistory.
OL,12,FHuge crowds attended a protest in
OL,13,FParis on Saturday calling for changes
OL,14,Fin societal attitudes towards consent.
OL,15,FThey carried placards with the slogan,
OL,16,F"shame must switch sides" - a
OL,17,Freference to a quote Gisele Pelicot
OL,18,Fmade during court proceedings.
